{"tid":53831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"結褵64年的夫妻 牽著彼此的手面對死亡","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T20:49:06.000Z","uid":35790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"439b0de6ff5a8fca06f1bc8a167d5076b6c5bb13","tid":53831,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"結褵64年的夫妻 牽著彼此的手面對死亡<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國田納西州有一對結縭將近64年的夫妻，日前丈夫因為腎衰竭住院，妻子則罹患嚴重的腦動脈瘤，最後兩人牽著彼此的手，在同個病房裡一起面對死亡，並在幾個小時之內相繼離世。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，丈夫特倫特（Trent Winstead）與妻子朵洛蕾斯（Dolores Winstead）在1950年代開始交往，特倫特從韓戰服役回國後，就決定向愛人求婚，兩人互相扶持到現在，共有2個孩子、3個孫子和8個曾孫。<br />\n<br />\n兩人原本要在明年的1月17日慶祝結婚64週年，但特倫特先是腎衰竭住院，治療過程也對他的心臟造成極大負擔，接著來院探視的朵洛蕾斯，則在12月7日晚間因腦動脈瘤發作而住院。醫院特別將兩人安排在同個病房，這對夫妻手牽著手笑著面對未來。<br />\n<br />\n到了12月9日晚間9時10分，朵洛蕾斯病重過世，特倫特被告知此事後，向著妻子送了一個飛吻，過了幾個小時，特倫特也闔上雙眼與世長辭。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprsv9c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprsv9c4.jpg&h=d070c122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1927768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1927768&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=91496a44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1927768&h=a69c574a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1927768</a>"},{"pid":"ae9938e402ce9f757e4defba7387095c1740c4f7","tid":53831,"uid":6038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1f828e1587aebf28acdefd99d16176f05e80de","tid":53831,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128ca26dc1ffb6498297e36ce54c259d9017f6ae","tid":53831,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"好浪漫但好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab2d05508d346cd4fd90bf55a208d361c5c096d","tid":53831,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f40d3e3545ec50e7881e8396fd90d115793ee4b2","tid":53831,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"the Notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f7895801ce523e86e6a33db88336b5edc53ca2","tid":53831,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f62c04c1eb8bf35b7278e70b1e28b20a1d4e892","tid":53831,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9526b8da6f99720a3ee1fa5355c50feddb0497e","tid":53831,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"好浪漫，對呢個遍地綠帽嘅世界又有返少少信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0483ae90f688b992037e7bc7dfa956c889feef95","tid":53831,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"世上最幸福既事"},{"pid":"69f4f368981e0621ebc101cbb320e82379dcad54","tid":53831,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世上最幸福既事</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7bc1aab98508e524a550a53e7ac6dd234e975686","tid":53831,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"搵到個陪伴至死既伴侶咁易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢地下世都可以一齊番白頭到老"},{"pid":"492a466164a8ad7099b5b34a121399ebd1a22b55","tid":53831,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"佢地就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b43eea0249cccb7232f53aac19cba64aae01348","tid":53831,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343a4d6a46b435395c2b5218131ce3fdbd9b6005","tid":53831,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"RIP <br />\n浪漫得黎帶點sad"},{"pid":"6fcea1c2c8e0e32620bd51d1f80458c20ca27da6","tid":53831,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c15d5457f036d601819a130f0982bb48668382a","tid":53831,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>the Notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c845a04d16c5d6ea07744fd8c7a0c455482ef5","tid":53831,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1f563b46e6ca7e41e61b399ccee1789f18c12e","tid":53831,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ff1e74b80e6111ec2ff6c605e513ba846615607","tid":53831,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"向至死不渝既愛情至敬<br />\n拜金女身上搵唔到呢d浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b03f21d3c94bcf0fde7df623cf689f29fc90592","tid":53831,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ca3706c3a677646acec30d33b5cb7ad48cf0dd","tid":53831,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"60歲的美國男子艾力（Eric Schmitt-Matzen）是一名職業聖誕老人，每年聖誕節來臨前，總是一身華麗的聖誕老人裝扮出席慶祝活動。談起聖誕老人的生涯，他回憶起一次完成了一名5歲病童的願望，病童最終在他懷內離世，令他心痛非常。<br />\n\r<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，艾力是名機械工程師，不過每年聖誕節前夕，他就會客串成聖誕老人出席慶祝活動，一年下來大概跑80場活動；一次下班返家後，他突然接到護士老友的緊急電話，對方懇求他到田納西州一間醫院，因一名5歲病危男童很想見到聖誕老人。<br />\n\r<br />\n他說，要裝扮成聖誕老人得花上一段時間，「但我的護士朋友告訴我，恐怕已經沒有時間了，請立即出門。」 幸虧他的鬍子是貨真價實的，因此掛了電話後，二話不說趕緊衝往醫院。到了醫院，他接過男童母親所準備的玩具禮物，並和男童的家屬說，「如果無法忍住不哭，那就別進去，因為只要有人落淚，我也會忍不住，這樣我的任務就失敗了。」最終大家都守在外頭，透過窗戶觀察病房內的一舉一動。"},{"pid":"8b67cd22a91bd5b35400b75dc2e0ddc28e9ebdcb","tid":53831,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"「當我走進去時，小男孩躺在那，全身無力感覺像是睡著了。」艾力說，他隨即坐在病床旁，一看男童睜開眼，立即和對方說，「我聽說你差點要錯過聖誕節了，這怎麼可能呢？！為什麼呢？因為你是我的頭號小精靈嘛。」<br />\n\r<br />\n男童：「真的嗎？」<br />\n\r<br />\n艾力：「那當然！」<br />\n\r<br />\n「他接過禮物後，連打開包裝的力氣也沒有，但當他看到禮物時，給了我一個很大的笑容，然而很快地又躺回床上。」<br />\n\r<br />\n男童：「他們說我會死，我怎麼知道我最終要去哪個地方呢？」<br />\n\r<br />\n艾力：「你能夠幫我一個忙嗎？」<br />\n\r<br />\n男童：「當然。」<br />\n\r<br />\n艾力：「當你去了那個地方，只要說自己是聖誕老人的頭號小精靈就可以了，他們會讓你進去的。」<br />\n\r<br />\n男童：「真的嗎？」<br />\n\r<br />\n艾力：「當然。」<br />\n\r<br />\n艾力說，5歲男童奮力坐起來擁抱他，又問了一個問題，「聖誕老人，你能幫我嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n當他準備開口回話時，小男童突然沒了呼吸，最終在他的懷裡死去。<br />\n\r<br />\n「我當過4年兵，看盡很多事情，但這場『活動』傷透我的心，我知道醫生與護士得天天面臨這些難關，回家的路上，我邊開著車，邊落淚。」艾力最後提到，「我在家呆坐了3天、花了一個禮拜去停止回想這起『活動』，我甚至想放棄擔任聖誕老人的角色，但當我在下一場活動時，看到孩子因我而歡笑時，我不禁想起醫院的那個小男童，也讓我明白這個角色的意義。」"},{"pid":"8c4b82e1d7b2ab11b0730c24c50cec8554db7a86","tid":53831,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1e405b0d107f7db2a1090b82670cfb6b7a9307a4","tid":53831,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:33:03.000Z","msg":"能夠一齊死算唔算都係一種幸福<br />\n<br />\n唔會有一邊扔低另一邊嘅事發生"}]}